这里以一个简单的登录功能为例来说明MVP的应用。

Model层：负责数据的处理和存储，例如用户的账号和密码等信息。

View层：负责显示视图，并处理用户的交互事件，例如登录按钮的点击事件。

Presenter层：作为模型和视图之间的中介，负责从Model层获取数据并告知View层进行显示，同时也负责处理视图传递过来的用户输入，比如输入账号密码后点击登录按钮，Presenter将会从Model层获取账号密码数据并进行验证，然后告知View层是否登录成功。

一个简单的MVP结构如下：

```
public interface LoginContract {
    interface View {
        void onLoginSuccess();
        void onLoginError(String errorMessage);
    }
    interface Presenter {
        void login(String account, String password);
    }
    interface Model {
        void login(String account, String password, ModelCallback callback);
        interface ModelCallback {
            void onSuccess();
            void onError(String errorMessage);
        }
    }
}

public class LoginPresenter implements LoginContract.Presenter {
    private LoginContract.View mView;
    private LoginContract.Model mModel;

    public LoginPresenter(LoginContract.View view) {
        mView = view;
        mModel = new LoginModel();
    }

    @Override
    public void login(String account, String password) {
        mModel.login(account, password, new LoginContract.Model.ModelCallback() {
            @Override
            public void onSuccess() {
                mView.onLoginSuccess();
            }

            @Override
            public void onError(String errorMessage) {
                mView.onLoginError(errorMessage);
            }
        });
    }
}

public class LoginModel implements LoginContract.Model {
    @Override
    public void login(String account, String password, ModelCallback callback) {
        // 假设这里面是从服务器获取账号信息，验证账号密码是否正确
        if ("test".equals(account) && "123456".equals(password)) {
            callback.onSuccess();
        } else {
            callback.onError("账号或密码错误");
        }
    }
}

public class LoginActivity extends AppCompatActivity implements LoginContract.View {
    private EditText mAccountEt;
    private EditText mPasswordEt;
    private Button mLoginBtn;
    private LoginContract.Presenter mPresenter;

    @Override
    protected void onCreate(@Nullable Bundle savedInstanceState) {
        super.onCreate(savedInstanceState);
        setContentView(R.layout.activity_login);
        mAccountEt = (EditText) findViewById(R.id.et_account);
        mPasswordEt = (EditText) findViewById(R.id.et_password);
        mLoginBtn = (Button) findViewById(R.id.btn_login);
        mPresenter = new LoginPresenter(this);
        mLoginBtn.setOnClickListener(new View.OnClickListener() {
            @Override
            public void onClick(View v) {
                String account = mAccountEt.getText().toString().trim();
                String password = mPasswordEt.getText().toString().trim();
                mPresenter.login(account, password);
            }
        });
    }

    @Override
    public void onLoginSuccess() {
        Toast.makeText(this, "登录成功", Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();
    }

    @Override
    public void onLoginError(String errorMessage) {
        Toast.makeText(this, errorMessage, Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();
    }
}
``` 

上面是一个简单的MVP实现，View层是LoginActivity，Model层是LoginModel，Presenter层是LoginPresenter。在具体实现的时候，可以根据实际业务需求进行扩展。

假设我们正在开发一个简单的待办事项应用程序，其中用户可以添加、删除和编辑任务。在MVC模式下，实现这个应用程序的主要部分将如下所述：

1. 模型(Model)：任务的数据。我们可以使用一个列表来管理任务，每个任务包含标题、日期和描述等信息。

```python
class Task:
    def __init__(self, title, date, description):
        self.title = title
        self.date = date
        self.description = description

class TaskList:
    def __init__(self):
        self.tasks = []

    def add_task(self, title, date, description):
        task = Task(title, date, description)
        self.tasks.append(task)

    def remove_task(self, task):
        self.tasks.remove(task)

    def edit_task(self, task, title=None, date=None, description=None):
        if title:
            task.title = title
        if date:
            task.date = date
        if description:
            task.description = description
```

2. 视图(View)：应用程序的用户界面。我们可以使用命令行界面呈现任务列表，让用户输入命令来添加、删除或编辑任务。

```python
class TaskView:
    def __init__(self):
        self.tasks = TaskList()

    def display_tasks(self):
        for task in self.tasks.tasks:
            print(task.title, task.date, task.description)

    def add_task(self):
        title = input('Task title: ')
        date = input('Task date: ')
        description = input('Task description: ')
        self.tasks.add_task(title, date, description)

    def remove_task(self):
        title = input('Task title to remove: ')
        for task in self.tasks.tasks:
            if task.title == title:
                self.tasks.remove_task(task)
                break

    def edit_task(self):
        title = input('Task title to edit: ')
        for task in self.tasks.tasks:
            if task.title == title:
                new_title = input('New title (press enter to skip): ')
                new_date = input('New date (press enter to skip): ')
                new_description = input('New description (press enter to skip): ')
                self.tasks.edit_task(task, new_title, new_date, new_description)
                break
```

3. 控制器(Controller)：模型和视图之间的中介。我们可以创建一个应用程序控制器，接受用户输入，并将其转发给相应的函数进行处理。

```python
class TaskController:
    def __init__(self):
        self.view = TaskView()

    def run(self):
        while True:
            print('Commands: add, remove, edit, display, exit')
            command = input('Enter a command: ')

            if command == 'add':
                self.view.add_task()
            elif command == 'remove':
                self.view.remove_task()
            elif command == 'edit':
                self.view.edit_task()
            elif command == 'display':
                self.view.display_tasks()
            elif command == 'exit':
                break
            else:
                print('Invalid command!')
```

在这个示例中，模型是代表任务列表的TaskList类，视图是代表用户界面的TaskView类，控制器是代表应用程序逻辑的TaskController类。通过使用MVC模式，我们可以将应用程序的不同部分分离开来，从而使应用程序更易于理解、维护和扩展。

Here is an example of a simple MVC (Model-View-Controller) pattern using JavaScript:

Model:

```
let data = [];

function addData(item) {
  data.push(item);
}

function getData() {
  return data;
}
```

View:

```
const view = (function() {
  const list = document.querySelector('#list');

  function render(items) {
    let html = '';
    items.forEach(item => {
      html += `<li>${item}</li>`;
    });
    list.innerHTML = html;
  }

  return {
    render
  };
})();
```

Controller:

```
const controller = (function(model, view) {
  const form = document.querySelector('#form');
  const input = document.querySelector('#item');

  function init() {
    form.addEventListener('submit', addItem);
    view.render(model.getData());
  }

  function addItem(e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    const item = input.value;
    model.addData(item);
    view.render(model.getData());
    input.value = '';
  }

  return {
    init
  };
})(model, view);

controller.init();
```

This example shows a simple to-do list application. The model represents the data of the application, which is an array of items. The view is responsible for rendering the data to the screen, and the controller handles user actions and updates the model and view accordingly. 

The init function in the controller sets up event listeners and calls the view to render the initial data. The addItem function is called when the user submits a new item through the form. The function adds the new item to the model, updates the view, and clears the input field.

